Properties.Description: Supports SideFX Labs Vertex Animation Textures Dynamic Remeshing (Fluid) mode. On the Material's Details panel, turn off Tangent Space Normal and set Num Customized UVs to 4. Surface texture UVs are only accessible if they have been exported from Houdini through some texture channels. (All native parameters are inside this Material Function. Create a Material Instance to gain access to the parameters. Avoid creating your own parameters outside this Material Function with names that clash with the parameter names inside this Material Function.)
